            "reviews": "“There are no revolutionary changes compared to its predecessor, but it's a nuanced improvement - in all the right places.”<br>85% – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.gamona.de/games/das-schwarze-auge-blackguards-2,test-pc:article,2587706,page-fazit.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Gamona</a><br><br>“Blackguards 2 is a step forward in every regard.”<br>82% – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.gamestar.de/spiele/blackguards-2/wertung/51231.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Gamestar</a><br><br>“Blackguards 2 is an immensely satisfying turn based strategy game that brings an enticing story and high-quality balanced combat to the table.”<br>8.8 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.hookedgamers.com/pc/blackguards_2/review/article-1395-2.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Hooked Gamers</a><br>",
